Practical – 4

Aim : Find Students whose age is greater than 20. Find students whose age is greater than 20 and score is less than 80. Find all students who live in “surat” or “vadodara”. Find all students whose course is BCA in the “students” collection.

Program :

Find Students whose age is greater than 20 db.faculties.find({}, { name: 1, department: 1, _id: 0 }) Output :












Find students whose age is greater than 20 and score is less than 80.

db.students.find({ age: { $gt: 20 }, score: { $lt: 80 } })

Output :



 
Find all Students who live in “surat” OR “vadodara” db.students.find({ city: { $in: ["Surat", "Vadodara"] } }) Output :


Find all students whose course is BCA in the “students” collection.

db.students.find({ course: "BCA" })
Output :

 
Practical – 5

Aim : Find all faculties aged 35 or older who live in Surat, from “faculties” collection. Sort the results of the previous query by age, in ascending order. Find faculties whose salary is greater than or equal to 30000 and less than 250000. Sort the results of the previous query by salary, in descending order.

Program :

Find all faculties aged 35 or older who live in Surat

db.faculties.find({ age: { $gte: 35 }, city: "Surat" })
Output :


Sort the results of the previous query by age (ascending order)
db.faculties.find({ age: { $gte: 35 }, city: "Surat" }).sort({ age: 1 })

Output :


 
Find faculties whose salary is ≥ 30000 and < 250000 db.faculties.find({ salary: { $gte: 30000, $lt: 250000 } }) Output :


Sort the results of the previous query by salary (descending order) db.faculties.find({ salary: { $gte: 30000, $lt: 250000 } }).sort({ salary: -1 }) Output :





 
Practical – 6

Aim : Find top five faculties with highest salary. Find faculties whose name starts with
“S”. Find faculties who are not from “Delhi”.

Program :

Find top five faculties with highest salary db.faculties.find().sort({ salary: -1 }).limit(5) Output :


Find faculties whose name starts with “S” db.faculties.find({ age: { $gte: 35 }, city: "Surat" }).sort({ age: 1 }) Output :








 
Find faculties who are not from “Delhi” db.faculties.find({ city: { $ne: "Delhi" } }) Output :










































 

Aim : Update a single document into “students” collection (ex:- age:25). Update all students enrolled in the “BSC” course by setting their batch 2025.

Program :

Find top five faculties with highest salary

db.students.updateOne(
{ name: "Ravi Kumar" }, // filter condition
{ $set: { age: 25 } } // update action
)

Output :


Update all students enrolled in the “BSC” course by setting their batch to 2025

db.students.updateMany(
{ course: "BSC" }, // filter condition
{ $set: { batch: 2025 } } // update action
)

Output :


 

Aim : Delete only one student named “Bob” from the “students” collection. Delete all
documents from the “students” collection where the course is “BA”.. Program :
Delete only one student named “Bob”

db.students.updateOne(
{ name: "Ravi Kumar" }, // filter condition
{ $set: { age: 25 } } // update action
)
Output :


Delete all documents where the course is “BA”

db.students.deleteMany({ course: "BA" })

Output :











 

